&lt;a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/659612963?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title" target="_blank"&gt;《艾尔登法环》DLC 黄金树幽影中新增了许多防具和套装，玩家对此款游戏体验感如何？&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
            
&lt;a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/532816443?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title" target="_blank"&gt;《艾尔登法环》或将推出 DLC ，你对此 DLC ，都有哪些期待？&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">安清</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 11:02:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/659503755/answer/3539966905</guid></item><item><title>现已可游玩，如何评价艾尔登法环DLC《黄金树幽影》？</title><link>http://www.zhihu.com/question/659482075/answer/3537454020?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title</link><description>&lt;p data-pid="pj3PvCbc"&gt;本回答现已修改&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4b26093e01c1f6968f631c20bcab1b3e_720w.jpg?source=b1748391?rss" data-rawwidth="2000" data-rawheight="1500" data-size="normal" data-watermark="original" data-original-src="v2-4b26093e01c1f6968f631c20bcab1b3e" data-watermark-src="v2-8efd910b093f7b11d6346ff742c24cd0" data-private-watermark-src="v2-934aa87efc6b73b82db07c3f7124d6aa" data-original-token="v2-4b26093e01c1f6968f631c20bcab1b3e" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="H_HH1MLg"&gt;未击败梅瑟莫前如果通过气流来到幽影亚坛后点亮通村吊桥赐福并往前走，游戏会提示某处大卢恩破碎，魅惑的力量消失&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9e03843ba6cbc0b1c80269e965c2e2e0_720w.jpg?source=b1748391?rss" data-rawwidth="960" data-rawheight="720" data-size="normal" data-watermark="original" data-original-src="v2-9e03843ba6cbc0b1c80269e965c2e2e0" data-watermark-src="v2-aa5339ce1c50cf79c63832ae63ef4ce7" data-private-watermark-src="v2-a9976a51a7fb791e51c91892bbc11ffa" data-original-token="v2-9e03843ba6cbc0b1c80269e965c2e2e0" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-766fc53604372d98a85fc97cf4b60cf7_720w.jpg?source=b1748391?rss" data-rawwidth="2000" data-rawheight="1500" data-size="normal" data-watermark="original" data-original-src="v2-766fc53604372d98a85fc97cf4b60cf7" data-watermark-src="v2-aea3168673b6e66c375f87911b02d2b7" data-private-watermark-src="v2-e5111ca47eaea512394ffb326cdabc4d" data-original-token="v2-766fc53604372d98a85fc97cf4b60cf7" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="mq5imc46"&gt;NPC会去各种地方，支线相当于以另一种方式推进，目前我找到的NPC都会帖在评论区，大家有知道去向的也可以补充&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="7h2QS_qF"&gt;所有NPC的支线只会在烧树后直接断（击败花朵圣女后的位置），击败梅瑟莫只影响角人支线，对其他NPC无影响&lt;/p&gt;
